description: It’s no longer a secret that Secret Sausage is one of the top sources of scrumptious street food in all of Seattle. Their savory selection includes Hot Links, German Frankfurters, Big Polish, and Mexican Chipotle Chorizo. You just choose which one you want nestled in a bolillo roll, then top it all off with their very own cream cheese, in-house made pepper sauce, or Salvadorian slaw. This food is so awesomely tasty, it’s just plain impossible to keep it confidential. Reveal the secret to your family and friends by having these carts come cater your next event. No matter the size of the crowd, Secret Sausage is equipped and ready to wow you all with their Seattle-inspired deliciousness.
name: Secret Sausage
